<P>
   SCIENCE/MEDICINE
</P>
<P>
   COXNET SCIHEALTH PAGE
</P>
<P>
   EDs: This is the CoxNet SCIHEALTH page for the current week.
This layout is now available.
</P>
<P>
   COXNET SCIHEALTH 0817 -- With summer here, women are inclinded
to wear for shorter skirts. But for many women, cellulite is a
problem that won't go away no matter the diet or amount of
exercise. Here are some methods women have tried to rid themselves
of the skin condition. (Anna, Palm Beach post) Art includes
3-column color photo of a woman's legs, a 1-column photo of a box
of cellulite cream and a 1-column photo of legs with cellulite.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: CELLULITE BOX -- A 2-column graphic showing what causes
cellulite.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: HEALTH NOTES -- Race and gender significantly affect the
quality of doctor-patient relationships _ and, consequently, may
affect the quality of health care patients receive, according to a
new study led by researchers at Johns Hopkins University in
Baltimore. (Lee Kim, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   LIFESTYLE
</P>
<P>
   WARNER-ON-WOOD _ ATLANTA _ Recently a correspondent on
rec.woodworking asked everybody how they got into woodworking and
some of the answers were rather striking. I'd like to share a few
with you. (Warner, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   ENTERTAINMENT
</P>
<P>
   MOVIES-SOLDIER _ Movie review: ``Universal Soldier: The
Return.'' It's another Jean-Claude Van Damme action flick, but this
one co-stars WCW wrestler and ex-Atlanta Falcon Bill Goldberg. Also
stars Michael Jai White. Movie opened At. 20 but was not
prescreened to critics. (Longino, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
10.
</P>
<P>
   DANCE _ Dance in the 20th century is the American century.
Despite its roots in Paris avant-garde art and politics, the
epicenter of dance moved across the Atlantic around 1930, when
Balanchine was brought here to build a ballet company; when Martha
Graham and the other founding mothers of modern dance established
their companies; when film and theatrical dance blossomed. This
survey of dance in the century will explain and illustrate the
theme of dance in the American century. (Green, Atlanta
journal-Constitution). 90. WITH PHOTO MONTAGE. FOR SUNDAY
</P>
