r k BC-MORSE-COLUMN-HNS &LR;      08-20 0859
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MORSE-COLUMN-HNS </SLUG>
  
 JOHN McCAIN: THE CANDIDATE WITH A PELLET GUN  c
 (EDS: Retransmitting to fix headline)   
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 EDS:  By ROB MORSE  
 c.1999 San Francisco Examiner  
<TEXT>
