<P>
   WALL-STREET-DORMITORY (New York) _ The residents of 45 Wall
Street are relatively young. They are urban. They are brazenly
professional. The converted office building in which they live, one
block from the New York Stock Exchange, has become known as an
upscale dormitory of sorts for armies of fresh college graduates,
who invade Wall Street from the country's premier universities. By
Jennifer 8. Lee.
</P>
