lobbyist. He has kept the same staff, the same travel schedule, the
same legislative agenda. He even totes the same trademark file
holder with ``SOLOMON'' emblazoned on the side. And the man who
heads the Solomon Group spends his week in Washington and returns
to upstate New York on weekends, just as he did during 20 years in
Congress. By JUDY HOLLAND.
