<P>
   MCCAIN (Seattle) _ Arizona Sen. John McCain is adopting a Navy
officer's tactics in the Republican presidential race, deciding the
rules and places of engagement and steering clear of battles he
cannot win. The former Vietnam POW arrived in Seattle Friday night
at the end of a week in which his campaign gained important
endorsements and a glimmer of voter recognition.
</P>
