<P>
   IRA_Pitfalls, Beneficiaries -- tk -- (BC-BIZ-IRA-FORMS-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   Avoiding pitfalls in naming IRA beneficiaries
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
</P>
</TEXT>
