<HEADLINE>
MUSIC INDUSTRY HITS FLAT NOTE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY DAVE MCNARY  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES -- The nation's music industry hit a flat note in
the first half of the year with shipments sliding 0.3 percent to
